result.title: RCC 2015 WarmUp Round
result.content: Russian Code Cup 2015 WarmUp Round will take place today at 10:00 UTC. Results of this round won't affect subsequent participation in RCC 2015, so this round can be viewed as a training before the qualification rounds. The contest lasts 2 hours, problem statements will be in Russian. The qualification rounds will take place on March 28th, April 25th and May 31st.
